snippet.title: NES Longplay [041] Quattro Arcade - CJ's Elephant Antics
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org 

Played By: Lemmy556

Nice arcade game for NES. This is one of those games that you can only find in Quattro series (unlicensed NES games). I played this with both elephant characters. This two playing thing turned useful, because peanut power was more stronger. I managed to finish the game with both characters. I also show how you can easily survive at volcanos. Its a glitch, not a cheat... -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
